The paper deals with image analysis and retrieval, which suggests that it could belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also points towards the deep learning (cs.DL) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV, cs.IR, and cs.DL, followed by cs.MM and cs.LG.
